{"id":"zohar","term":"Zohar","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Brightness. (1.) The father of Ephron the Hittite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 23:8\">Gen. 23:8</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) One of the sons of Simeon (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 46:10\">Gen. 46:10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:15\">Ex. 6:15</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 23:8","Genesis 46:10","Exodus 6:15"]}